      <title>朝鲜抨击卢比奥“粗鲁”言论，誓言予以强硬回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/north-korea-slams-rubio-s-coarse-remarks-vows-tough-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜强烈谴责美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥最近将平壤描述为“流氓”国家，并誓言“绝不容忍”华盛顿的任何挑衅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/north-korea-slams-rubio-s-coarse-remarks-vows-tough-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:48:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称对欧盟征收关税“肯定会发生”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-says-tariffs-will-definitely-happen-with-european-union</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他“肯定”会对欧盟征收新的关税，并重申对美国与欧盟的贸易逆差以及他认为欧盟对美国汽车和农产品进口不足的抱怨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-says-tariffs-will-definitely-happen-with-european-union</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:41:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言因土地政策切断对南非的援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-pledges-to-cut-aid-to-south-africa-over-land-expropriation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，美国将因南非的土地征用政策停止向其提供援助，这引发兰特的抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-pledges-to-cut-aid-to-south-africa-over-land-expropriation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:58:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普“关税大举” 加拿大采取危机应对措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/donald-trump-s-tariffs-spur-crisis-response-from-canada-banks-and-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统签署命令对美国从加拿大购买的几乎所有产品征收 25% 的关税后，加拿大政府官员和商界领袖采取了与新冠疫情类似的危机应对措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/donald-trump-s-tariffs-spur-crisis-response-from-canada-banks-and-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:46:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税如何摧毁美洲经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-02-02/who-wins-in-a-trade-war-how-trump-tariffs-threaten-companies-us-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过数周的威胁，北美贸易战终于爆发。企业和投资者正在为后果做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-02-02/who-wins-in-a-trade-war-how-trump-tariffs-threaten-companies-us-growth</guid>
